	(text "Program Fast-Charge Safety Timer (TMR):\nRTMR = tMAXCHG / (10 × KTMR )\nKTMR = 48 s/kΩ from the electrical characteristics table.\nRTMR = (6.25 hr × 3600 s/hr) / (10 × 48 s/kΩ) = 46.8 kΩ ->  46.4 kΩ\n"
